### 7. URL Routing Design

```
Public HLS (no auth):
GET /public/{content_id}/playlist.m3u8
GET /public/{content_id}/segment_{n}.ts

Private HLS (JWT required):
GET /private/{content_id}/playlist.m3u8  # Authorization: Bearer <jwt>
GET /private/{content_id}/segment_{n}.ts

Health endpoints:
GET /health  # Liveness
GET /ready   # Readiness
GET /metrics # Prometheus (port 9090)
```

